  "title": "Mars's Enchanted Book Textures",
  "description": "Changes textures of enchanted books for better clarity",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XLhWGhC.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/different-textures-for-enchanted-books\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/452537?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/different-textures-for-enchanted-books\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/different-textures-for-enchanted-books?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This resource pack gives every enchanted book a unique texture, making it much easier to find the one you need at a glance. Each book’s cover color is themed based on the type of enchantment and the items it can be applied to, helping you organize and identify them quickly in your inventory or storage.</p></center>\n <ul>\n  <li><strong>Since 1.21.5</strong> You do not need any additional mods</li>\n  <li><strong>From 1.20.5 to 1.21.3</strong> I would recommend using <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-enchanted-books-hotfix\">CIT: Hotfix for Enchanted Books</a></li>\n  <li><strong>From 1.13 to 1.20.4</strong> You should use any mod which supports the CIT standard like <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-resewn\">CIT Resewn</a> or <a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\">Optifine</a></li>\n  <li>You can also run this as a <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/enchanted-books-from-mars\">standalone mod</a></li>\n</ul> \n<center>\n<br />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Examples of the new textures</h2>\n<p>Resource Packs <b>ON</b><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ClzoG9Q.png\" width=\"460\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gF6wPij.png\" width=\"460\" /></p>\n<p>Resource Packs <b>OFF</b><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/buQW2Sc.png\" width=\"460\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qg9kIju.png\" width=\"460\" /></p>\n</center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>\n",
